title: muslim
content:
Muslim
ˈmʊzlɪm,ˈmʌz-,-s-/
noun
noun: Muslim; plural noun: Muslims; noun: Moslem; plural noun: Moslems
  1. 1.
    a follower of the religion of Islam.
adjective
adjective: Muslim; adjective: Moslem
  1. 1.
    relating to Muslims or their religion.
Origin
early 17th century: from Arabic, active participle of 'aslama (see Islam).
